      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JOCK FROM IBROX (1) stalked the lead from a low draw then burst clear to score (29.66) at this track in a Maiden over 515m. Comes through a solid form race last start. Can make it back-to-back wins. DEADLY VENOM (8) had been in super honest form hitting the frame two times on end before finishing fourth (30.84) at Gosford last time. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Bold showing expected. TEQUILA GIRL (2) is having her first start around this course. Missed the frame last time when 4th and beaten 5.5 lengths (25.63) at Maitland. Smart beginner who should take advantage of the low draw. Likely to be thereabouts. HUNTERVIEW JACK (6) was unplaced here last start but gets his chance to atone.",
